OL,5, Sports Direct owner Frasers Group is   
OL,6, buying Gieves & Hawkes, the historic   
OL,7, Savile Row tailor, the BBC has learned.
OL,9,FThe Frasers Group's chief executive    
OL,10,Fsaid the move secured "a long-term     
OL,11,Ffuture" for the 250-year-old firm.     
OL,13,FThe retail giant, which was founded by 
OL,14,FMike Ashley, emerged as a potential    
OL,15,Fbuyer of Gieves & Hawkes in September. 
OL,17,FIt is understood all five of Gieves &  
OL,18,FHawkes's UK stores will be part of the 
OL,19,Fdeal, including the flagship location  
OL,20,Fat Number 1 Savile Row in London.      
